divs: Sighting Detailsi was outside in Oshawa looking at stars when in the NE sky were 2 very close ufo's flashing very quick different colours then traveled slow west then 1 turned around and went back and another was in the East sky and while filming it i wanted to get the street light in the picture to show exactly where it was but when i looked at the video beside the street light was a hovering ufo with red blue white flashes and multiple orbs going into it my batteries ran out so i went in
Object Flight Path: Stationary,Straight-line path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering,Other,Unknown
trends: There have been 12 other sightings in Oshawa

Summary: multiple ufo's blinking very fast different colours coming from NE to W then a couple changed direction and 1 was hovering very close i have vid
